ation.                            Visit Us  Crumley Hall        UNT Housing 1621 W. Highland St. Denton, TX 76201         Mail Us   UNT Housing 1155 Union Circle #311310 Denton, TX 76203 Phone: (940) 565-2610 Fax: (940) 369-8764       Contact Us   (940) 565-2610 housinginfo@unt.edu Technical issues?                   Site last updated on May 06, 2017  Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home     Site last updated on May 06, 2017 | Important Links           
